raw_text = "~ start
## 5:40pm ish time
do Story.set_location(\"mabels_room\")
Mabel: Hey babe
Mabel: I just got home
Player: Hiya
Mabel: I'm soooo nervous about this shoot omg 😩
Mabel: I've been thinking about it all day
do echo_set([\"109\"])
Mabel: I don't know what to do!!
if Story.has_flag(\"LOVE\"):
	Player: Don't worry, I'll be there too!
	Player: And I don't know what I need to really do either haha
	Mabel: I'm a little glad to hear that 🥹
	Mabel: We can be lost together hehe 😁
	Player: For sure!
else:
	Player: Don't worry, Caleb will be there!
	Mabel: Yeah, I feel like he's just really good at everything and never complains 🥹
	Mabel: He's just amazing
	Mabel: I wish I could learn from him
	Player: And Naomi works hard all the time too
	Mabel: Omg you're right, aren't they such a cute couple??
	Mabel: I hope they have time for each other 😣
do echo_clear()
if Story.has_flag(\"Alice1\"):
	Mabel: Also..
	Mabel: img: mabel/110
	Mabel: You're helping Alice right?
	Mabel: You're so sweet for that 🥺
	Player: Trying my best!
	Mabel: I hope you can make friends with her at least
	Mabel: I remember I was a bit like her
	Player: You still hide behind your mom's skirt 😂
	Mabel: Shush 😳
	Mabel: Omg you always bring that up 🤣 I hate you
	Player: 😁
	Player: I'm not really an expert so I hope I can be of help
if Story.has_flag(\"Paige1\"):
	Mabel: Also..
	Mabel: You're helping Paige?? 🙄
	Mabel: I hope it's gonna be okay and that she doesn't drive you crazy 😭
	Player: Not sure what to expect 😅
	Player: Just trying to be helpful is all
	Mabel: Okay but if she's mean to you just tell me, and I'll be all mean back to her 😠
	Mabel: img: mabel/111
	Player: I will 😆
	Mabel: 😇
	Player: I'm not really an expert so I hope I can be of help
Mabel: Alright I'm going to watch some videos on my tablet and try not to think about this modeling thing lol
Mabel: Talk to you later babe! 🥰
Player: Night!
do social_post(\"naomi_caleb_match\")
=> END"
metadata/dialogue_manager_version = "3.7.1"
